    "description": "UNIRITA Inc. provides software and solutions for information technology (IT) systems operation in Japan and internationally. The company offers auttit, a SaaS-based job management cloud service; DigiSheet and The Staff-V, which are personnel management cloud services; and Waha!Transformer. Its products LMIS, a lifecycle management product for IT services; A-AUTO, an automatic job scheduling and monitoring system; Sky-Eye Tribune, a monitoring system that includes resource management, network management, server management, and desktop management; TIA Report, a total information analysis report system; BSP-RM, a multiplatform report management system; Exentry, a data entry system; Be.Learning, an e-learning system for IT systems operations management; A-SPOOL, a report system management; and A-LOG, a job log and system log management system. The company also provides related consulting and technical support services. It serves corporate clients and businesses. UNIRITA Inc. was incorporated in 1982 and is headquartered in Minato, Japan."
